i havent been on here for a while for reasons of my own. but im beging to relize how stupid we all are. do me a favor and ask yourselfs these questions....
what makes you happy? 
what makes you sad?
what makes you angry or mad?
what makes you giggel and laugh?
what makes you exited?
what makes you afraid?
what makes you cry?
what makes your heart bleed?
what makes you joyus?
what makes you love?
what makes you jelous?
what makes you wrathful?
what makes you hurt?


all of us and anser theses questions and more. for all that makes us feel good why dont we do it more. we seem to forget what makes us happy. but we always seem to make ourselfs hurt. no matter how far life gets you up we always bring ourselfs down. i dont understany why we would do that. so what if life gives you crap do things that make you happy. stop being stuborn and saying it wont work. if you dont in the end your life will fail you will fail and then youll wonder why your life wasnt happy and regret not even trying. if we all tryed to makes ourselfs feel happyer everyone around up will feel slightly more happy. i know that the friends that are true to me make me happy when they are. so why do we become greedy and be sad with no joy. we hurt everyone eles around us.i have had my heart bleed and i know i dont like it one bit. so all i can do is do things that make me happy. or ill fall in darkness and be consumed my hate and sadness and nevery be happy agin but forever be hurting.
